high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn left and walk up to the middle of the couch.
Pick up the phone off of the seat of the couch.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the brown chair with a credit card on its seat.
Place the phone on the seat of the brown chair to the right of the credit card.
Turn left and walk over to the wooden coffee table.
Pick up the phone that is on the wooden coffee table.
Turn left and walk over to the brown chair with the phone and credit card on its seat.
Place the phone on the brown chairs seat to the left of the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Move two phones to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Move to the couch to the right of you
pick up a phone from the couch
move to the arm chair behind you
put the phone on the chair
move to the coffee table to the left of you
pick up a phone from the table
move to the arm chair to the left of you
put the phone on the chair
anns.task_desc: Put two phones on the arm chair next to the simple chair.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the couch.
Pick up the cell phone on the couch.
Turn around and go to the cloth chair in the corner.
Put the cell phone on the cloth chair.
Turn around and go to the coffee table.
Pick up the cell phone on the coffee table.
Turn around and go to the cloth chair in the corner.
Put the cell phone on the cloth chair.
anns.task_desc: Move two cells phones to the cloth chair in the corner.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the front of the couch.
Pick up the cell phone that's to the right of the keys.
Turn left and walk to the brown chair with the credit card.
Put the cell phone on the chair in front of the credit card.
Turn left and walk to the coffee table.
Pick up the cell phone next to the tissue box.
Turn around and walk back to the brown chair.
Put the cell phone down to the left of the other cell phone.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the couch move so you are facing the center right of the couch.
Pick up the remote that is on the couch.
With the remote in hand go to the brown chair that is to the right of the wooden brown chair.
Place the remote on top right of the item that is on the chair.
Turn and go to the coffee table on the opposite side of the couch.
Pick up the cell phone that is on the coffee table.
Go to the brown chair that is to the right of the wooden brown chair with the phone in hand.
Place the cell phone on top of the object that is on the chair on the left side of it.
Turn around and walk to the front of the couch and stand in front of the cell phone on the couch.
Pick up the cell phone to the right of the keys.
Turn around and walk to the brown chair to the right of the wooden chair.
Place the cell phone to the right of the credit card on the brown chair.
Turn and walk to the coffee table that's in front of the couch, and face the cell phone and the tissue box.
Pick up the cell phone to the left of the tissue box on the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the brown chair that has the first cell phone on it.
Place the cell phone to the left of the first cell phone on the brown chair.
